</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>Jobs' Biography: Thoughts On Life, Death And Apple</b>   <b data-is-speakable>After Steve Jobs was diagnosed with cancer, he asked Walter Isaacson to write his biography. The new book tells the personal story of the man behind the personal computer — from his childhood in California to his thoughts on family, friends, death and religion.</b>
</div>
<div id="wrapper">
